milestones.description: Ravi Shastri has scored 2 hundreds in ODIs, the most for IND breaking Vengsarkar's record
Ravi Shastri and Srikkanth's 188-run partnership is IND's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 123 between Engineer and Gavaskar
Ravi Shastri and Srikkanth's 188-run partnership is the highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 182 between Rick McCosker and Alan Turner
Ravi Shastri and Srikkanth's 188-run partnership is IND's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 143 between Sandeep Patil and Vengsarkar
